  "type": "PRACTICE",
  "sourceNotes": "Adapted from Day 38 of MONEY: A 12-Week Tapping Program (Rebecca J Page, 2025), \"Allow savings to grow effortlessly.\" Tapping framework: Gary Craig's Emotional Freedom Technique (EFT), in use since the mid-1990s, building on Roger Callahan's Thought Field Therapy.",
